name: Teemo's Jungle Timer for League of Legends
name_original: Teemo's Jungle Timer for League of Legends
description:
This is the Newest Version 3.0 of Teemo's Jungle Timer!

The only jungle timer in the App Store with the new updated flash cooldown time of 5 minutes.

The simplest and most user friendly League of Legends, Summoner's Rift, timer currently in the App Store.

Timers include:
- Dragon
- Baron
- Both Red and Blue Buffs
- Teleport Summoner Spell
- 2 Flash Summoner Spells
- 2 Sight Ward Timers
- 1 Vision Ward Timer
